IMAPAccount gmail-lniz
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User lniz.cloud@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.secrets/gmail-lniz.gpg"
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.2 +1.3
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-lniz-remote
Account gmail-lniz

MaildirStore gmail-lniz-local
Path ~/mail/lniz-cloud/
Inbox ~/mail/lniz-cloud/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail-lniz
Far :gmail-lniz-remote:
Near :gmail-lniz-local:
Patterns *
Create Near
Expunge None
SyncState *
Sync Full
CopyArrivalDate yes




